item.title: Arrays
item.description: Two Sum ðŸ“— Problem Given an array of integers nums and an integer target, return indices of the two numbers such that they add up to target. You may assume that each input would have *exactly* one solution, and you may not use the same element twice. You can return the answer in any order. Solution The concept here is to have a dictionary that stores the current value and the key, and the index as the value.
